<div class="page">
  <div class="row">
    <img class="how-it-works-header-image" src="<%= image_url('page/mugs_small.png') %>" alt="bottles">
  </div>

  <h3>How it Works</h3>

  <div class="row">
    <h5><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>&nbsp;Buying</h5>
    <p>PromoExchange works! As the leading online exchange for promotional products, our marketplace brings Buyers and qualified Sellers together, streamlines the bidding process, and provides immediate savings. More savings means more power for your promotional products budget.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <h5><span class="fa-stack fa-lg">
      <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-inverse fa-stack-1x">1</i>
    </span>Register as a single user or as a part of a larger organization</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Using PromoExchange is free for all Buyers. There are no hidden fees!</li>
      <li>At checkout, the price you see will always be your “all-in” price, including shipping costs.</li>
      <li>Welcome to the PromoExchange community! We’re excited for you to be a part of the premier place to source promotional products. As a PromoExchange member, you are able to buy your favorite promotional products while saving time and money!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <h5><span class="fa-stack fa-lg">
      <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-inverse fa-stack-1x">2</i>
    </span>Create Your Listing</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Find the promotional product you would like to buy in our product catalog of over 8,000 products. Don’t see your item? <a href="/support">Let us know!</a> We’ll add it to the catalog!</li>
      <li>Upload your logo, set the date you need the items by, and select your payment method.</li>
      <li>Invite any Sellers you know and trust to participate. Thanks for introducing them to the team... they will receive pricing discounts and access to other Auctions thanks to your invite!</li>
      <li>Start your Auction and watch the bidding begin!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <h5><span class="fa-stack fa-lg">
          <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
          <i class="fa fa-inverse fa-stack-1x">3</i>
        </span>
        Select the Winner</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Choose the bid you want at any time. Many of our Sellers have already placed bids with their best pricing for all items in our product catalog. You can choose from bids posted by your invited Sellers or from those recommended by other Buyers in the PromoExchange community. It is completely up to you!</li>
      <li>If you choose a Seller you invited to the Auction, you will pay them directly according to the same terms by which you always pay them. If you choose another Seller, you will pay for the order via an escrow account held by PromoExchange. Though we expect your order to always meet our standards, you will receive a full refund should it not.</li>
      <li>Now your order is in production and you can sit back and relax (or at least focus on more important aspects of your life or business)! You will receive frequent progress alerts and tracking information from now until you get your order.</li>
    </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a class="btn btn-success hiw_btn" href="/dashboards" role="button">Start Buying</a>
